videos.description: Kansas State's Kylin Hill takes the handoff for a big 47-yard run to get a first down.
videos.headline: KSU's Hill breaks out for 47-yard run

videos.description: Kansas State's Skylar Thompson is hit hard on the blind side and loses the ball, but it is ruled an incomplete pass.
videos.headline: KSU's Skylar Thompson hit hard from behind

videos.description: Mississippi State's Brian Cole  leaps over KSU kicker Blake Lynch for a 37-yard kickoff return.
videos.headline: Cole leaps over kicker on return

videos.description: Mississippi State's Nick Fitzgerald connects with Kylin Hill, who leaps over a defender for a touchdown to give Mississippi State the lead.
videos.headline: Hill leaps over defender for 16-yard TD

videos.description: Mississippi State's Nick Fitzgerald runs for 43 yards and picks up a big first down.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald breaks out for 30-yard first down

videos.description: KSU's Skylar Thompson  is hit hard in the pocket and is picked off by Errol Thompson.
videos.headline: Thompson hit hard, throws INT

videos.description: Mississippi State's Kylin Hill breaks out for a 28-yard run up the middle and dives for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Kylin Hill dives for 28-yard TD

videos.description: KSU's Kylin Hill takes off through the middle for a huge 52-yard gain.
videos.headline: Hill bursts through the defense for 52-yard gain

videos.description: Kansas State's Nick Fitzerald connects with a diving Austin Williams for the 13-yard touchdown pass.
videos.headline: KSU's Williams dives for TD catch

videos.description: Kansas State's Skylar Thompson is swallowed up in the backfield by Mississippi State's Fletcher Adams.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Adams comes up with big time sack

videos.description: Kansas Sate lineman Wyatt Hubert tips Nick Fitzgerald's pass and comes up with the interception and 11-yard return.
videos.headline: KSU lineman Hubert tips pass for INT

videos.description: Skylar Thompson finds a stretched out Dalton Schoen for a 23-yard touchdown pass.
videos.headline: KSU's Schoen stretches out for TD grab

videos.description: Kylin Hill plows his way through the Kansas State defense for his second touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Hill powers through the defense for 2nd TD
